lead_paragraph: Crowd trouble marred West Ham United's continued resurgence as fans clashed at the London Stadium near the end of their 2-1 League Cup derby victory over Chelsea on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Unacceptable Says Bilic as Crowd Trouble Mars West Ham Victory
